  "title": "Administrative Assistant (Architecture/Interior Design)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide administrative assistance on architecture/interior design consultancy services</li><li>Manage phone calls, emails and coordinate meetings</li><li>Liaise between clients, consultants and other external stakeholders to ensure smooth running of projects</li><li>Prepare and organize project documentation, correspondence, meeting materials</li><li>Support with ad-hoc administrative duties</li></ul><p><strong>What we are looking for:</strong></p><ul><li>High School Diploma or equivalent</li><li>Proficient with Microsoft Office (PowerPoint, Word, Excel etc.)</li><li>Proficient in English (written and spoken)</li></ul><p><strong>Good to have:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience with administrative work</li><li>Knowledge or experience with design (architecture and interior design)</li><li>Familiarity with Adobe Photoshop</li><li>Proficiency in Mandarin (spoken)</li></ul>",
